{"tid":531314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【僭建醜聞】團體網上聯署　促鄭若驊辭職","createTime":"2018-01-16T15:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T12:15:20.000Z","uid":103759,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7d7d2e8320014f9cdfb81ba5802d84302abfdd0f","tid":531314,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"律政司司長鄭若驊上任後爆出僭建醜聞。有團體近日發起網上聯署，質疑鄭若驊未能夠令所有港人相信其品格及能力，要求鄭若驊辭職。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信指鄭若驊被揭發僭建，先後以不同的說辭支吾以對，又質疑身位土木工程師及資深大律師的她，不會不知道自己單位有僭建物：「一個不盡不實的大律師，如何令人相信能夠擔任律政司司長，能夠秉公處理所有職務？鄭若驊未能夠令所有香港人相信其品格和能力，能夠捍衞香港的法治。」他們要求鄭若驊辭職，以守護香港人對法治的信念。<br />\n<br />\n該聯署是由團體「匯政衞言」發起，其FB介簡自是稱一個「社區為本的政黨」。早前何君堯公開稱對港獨人士「殺無赦」，匯政衞言亦有發起聯署要求香港律師會對何君堯展開紀律聆訊。<br />\n立場新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%83%AD%E5%BB%BA%E9%86%9C%E8%81%9E-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E4%BF%83%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2583%25AD%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E9%2586%259C%25E8%2581%259E-%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E9%25A9%258A%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E8%2581%25B7%2F&d=Dxp51rT0QgXQJyfURqq9Q%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=68204ee3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2583%25AD%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E9%2586%259C%25E8%2581%259E-%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E9%25A9%258A%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E8%2581%25B7%2F&h=47342288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%83%AD%E5%BB%BA%E9%86%9C%E8%81%9E-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E4%BF%83%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7/</a><br />\n==========================<br />\n==========================<br />\n一人一簽名　聯署要求鄭若驊辭任律政司司長<br />\n鄭若驊位於屯門大欖的獨立屋被揭發有僭建，先後以不同的說辭支吾以對。鄭若驊身位土木工程師，亦是資深大律師，豈會不知道自己單位有僭建物。而且，有傳媒揭發其單位是在鄭若驊購入後才出現僭建。<br />\n<br />\n一個不盡不實的大律師，如何令人相信能夠擔任律政司司長，能夠秉公處理所有職務？鄭若驊未能夠令所有香港人相信其品格和能力，能夠捍衞香港的法治。<br />\n<br />\n所以，為了守護香港人對法治的信念，鄭若驊必需辭職。<br />\n<br />\n發起人　匯政衞言<br />\n<br />\n聯署 Link: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1SqyV74Kb4xhC-gQm62r_s47WF7OQl_n4FVcsOcXkviM/viewform?edit_requested=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1SqyV74Kb4xhC-gQm62r_s47WF7OQl_n4FVcsOcXkviM%2Fviewform%3Fedit_requested%3Dtrue&d=Dxp51rT0QgXQJyfURqq9Q%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=cc50f917\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1SqyV74Kb4xhC-gQm62r_s47WF7OQl_n4FVcsOcXkviM/viewform?edit_requested=true</a>"},{"pid":"81a180fa4340bfa14b5d8e20d282bac37172e33e","tid":531314,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T10:34:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f32591ce36f15faad799577032bdfd707df2193","tid":531314,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T10:41:42.000Z","msg":"自推上熱門"},{"pid":"cc2c5762df4e8e30dfb34a8fad4bc9feb945964a","tid":531314,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T11:18:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98aff64463446221068957b20020f0c448f6df70","tid":531314,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:02:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e924e34261427d401b2fcab17f017dcb0ff69782","tid":531314,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"奶共傳媒點撐?"},{"pid":"977d0edbb1e8af783da3af7badbe1382b5c37c46","tid":531314,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e924e34261427d401b2fcab17f017dcb0ff69782","tid":531314,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"奶共傳媒點撐?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:09:28.000Z","msg":"盲?"},{"pid":"a29b7fdcb777a60b837a075318464590b08a28a5","tid":531314,"uid":60959,"